      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "DEVIOUS MINDS (10) has been freshened since the Nutrien series where she placed in both rounds, beaten less than 6m into third in the Listed 3F final last time out. Draws on the back row but is two for two here so looks well placed. SUNLIGHT STRIDE (4) broke the maiden in good style last start, leading to score by 3.3 metres at this circuit and distance last week. Likely to get the favours from another nice draw and could go on with it now. MICKEYS RUN (3) is building in fitness and is right in contention after coming from tougher barriers to finish in the placings in his two outings at Penrith since a spell. ROCK WITH THE BEST (11) may need some luck from this draw but deserves respect after missing narrowly at Wagga last start.",
